my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-humanization.md:149:## Anti-patterns to reject (built into CI)
my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-humanization.md:151:- **Random-as-expression.** Gaussian jitter without structured deviation. Ljung-Box must reject white-noise null on tempo and velocity series.
my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-humanization.md:153:- **Forgetting machine identity.** If a rule leaks onto grid-locked voices, the render fails the role-filter gate.
my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-humanization.md:157:- **Dead-silence failure.** A 2-minute melodic passage with no rests ≥200 ms fails — silence is a first-class voice.

